{"tid":1831913,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂46討論區#294: 耐心等待25單","createTime":"2020-01-20T18:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T18:37:41.000Z","uid":63229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8aca40b8a502602ff4d357752894b0668b71275f","tid":1831913,"uid":63229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:27:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[b]乃Po呼籲: <br />\n<br />\n白花幾時可以再合體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7z5kbt0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7z5kbt0.png&h=647c0d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EpCR2Bg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEpCR2Bg.png&h=76ae881d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OOxKDba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOOxKDba.jpg&h=f6c4743d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hpxCdKx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhpxCdKx.jpg&h=c65c6252&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eSEXYbg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeSEXYbg.png&h=131a57be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[red]乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一至四期生在內，團體目前共有43名成員，而隊長為秋元真夏。其與2015年8月21日成立的櫸坂46、以及2019年2月11日自櫸坂46獨立的日向坂46，構成大型偶像組合系列「坂道系列」。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團名取自坐落東京都赤坂地區乃木坂的「SME乃木坂大樓」，該建築為所屬唱片公司日本索尼音樂的前辦公大樓之一。根據秋元康所說，<span style=\"color: red;\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成員名單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nogizaka46.com%2Fmember%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9xZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=2f0eaf17\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/</a><br />\n<br />\n[size=6]<span style=\"color: purple;\">[center]-NEWS-</div><br />\n</span></span><br />\n[size=4]<div style=\"text-align: center;\">乃木坂46 24thシングル<br />\n「夜明けまで強がらなくてもいい」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EeYNpoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEeYNpoM.png&h=1c0202b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n桜井玲香2nd写真集『視線』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p0h8R54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp0h8R54.jpg&h=dc9fd472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n衛藤美彩フォトブック『Decision』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1uOBES.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1uOBES.jpg&h=033ccd13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山下美月1st写真集『忘れられない人』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2020年1月21日發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dTTDep3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdTTDep3.jpg&h=9c3fba6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堀未央奈2nd写真集『タイトル未定』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2020年発売</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pLrGQD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pLrGQD.jpg&h=7a8f974b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46成員列表 (最新)</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55jjZ5r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55jjZ5r.png&h=49fb8707&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNvbRca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNvbRca.png&h=4cbd3c30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAQ7pxc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAQ7pxc.png&h=cb84f029&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0CDQniT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0CDQniT.png&h=e765757c&s={SIZE}\" /></div>[/size=4］<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnogizaka46-dc.com%2Fsort%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9xZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=e9198d1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/nogizaka46sort.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkeyakizaka46style.com%2Fsort%2Fnogizaka46sort.html&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9xZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=b92b5b70\" target=\"_blank\">http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/nogizaka46sort.html</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購,，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員,但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n直接飛去日本或中國參加握手會、演唱會、見面會，但不要幻想會再來港，因香港已經柒出國際。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。<br />\n<br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d75b9c76321962e98d26a048ab64f3b0cadb3b4","tid":1831913,"uid":189666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:29:44.000Z","msg":"死仔  推PO圖都唔貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55346a4381a822b9881b1ccf59541c65d301cb3","tid":1831913,"uid":149912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GHCbicD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGHCbicD.jpg&h=3ccabf1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RjD566n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjD566n.jpg&h=308895ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BrUhdMp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBrUhdMp.jpg&h=3a8fc5e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pPCR2EL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpPCR2EL.jpg&h=5745f2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白花老公留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08fb83f57ff666e0c6e73dc120068a8cc4820da","tid":1831913,"uid":189666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yTKtkrC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyTKtkrC.jpg&h=87fe466f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nLM"},{"pid":"d53607486c0e22b7f42c9217fad400a992d62d08","tid":1831913,"uid":285411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XxJmFrA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXxJmFrA.jpg&h=48c914f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜半劉明"},{"pid":"0f8a518f33a38e6c